Directory structe start with base DN. it is the root where we can create first entity
1) DN name
2)ldap split DNS name with "." deliminator. Each of the splited value will have an entity using domain object and it has DC attribute as RDN
DC=domain component.
Factore influence directory Tree:-
1)  Enterprise structure - if organisatin in different geographical region
2) Application to be used - either for simple data storage or for authentication.
3) Replication machnisam
4) customised object classed as per requirement.

How to frame DN of user in directory structure:-
RDN + path to base dn from RDN + base dn
